<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[#0C447C] mb-12 text-center">Three commands. That's it.</h2>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#E6F1FB] text-[#185FA5] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">1</div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-mono text-sm bg-slate-900 text-green-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg mb-3 inline-block">lodestar start</div>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Load context from your last session. Your AI knows what was decided, what patterns are established, and where you left off.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#E6F1FB] text-[#185FA5] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">2</div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-mono text-sm text-slate-500 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg mb-3 inline-block border border-slate-200">... code ...</div>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Work normally. Commit as you go. Lodestar tracks changes in the background — no interruptions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-[#E6F1FB] text-[#185FA5] flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">3</div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-mono text-sm bg-slate-900 text-green-400 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg mb-3 inline-block">lodestar end</div>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Done for the day. Lodestar synthesizes your session into a <code class="text-xs bg-slate-100 px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono">.lodestar.md</code> — decisions, patterns, rejected approaches, and exactly where to pick up.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
